###
## drumTruck INSTALLATION
##

ffmpeg
	. http://ffmpegx.com/download.html
	. `nanopads` requires ffmpeg to convert all audio files in a directory to 44.1khz WAVs

afplay
	. `truck` uses OSX-native `afplay` to play directories of files

install.sh
	. launch Terminal and run ./install.sh
	. relaunch Terminal for your new PATH (~/.bash_profile) to take effect

Enjoy!
-c3w
